markets.name: 1X2
markets.oddsDescription:
Standard 1X2: Predict the final outcome of the match in regular time. The bet offers three possible outcomes: 1 (home team wins); X (teams draw), 2 (away team wins)
 Fantasy 1X2: Predict which team/player will score most goals in their respective matches. If both teams/players score the same number of goals, the winning selection will be X.
